<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The first argument for the constructor is 'label', which is rarely used by the current use cases of the gd:where element.  Calendar, the current major service using this element, only generally uses the 'valueString' attribute.</p>

<p>Before the Calendar extension is heavily used, and before ZF 1.0 is released, I recommend re-ordering the constructor arguments to have valueString as the first argument.</p>

